replies.body:
Every time you nerf a class's rush item it feels like you leave that class without an item to rush properly.

Top lane tanks: {{item:3068}} 
Enchanters: {{item:3174}} , then {{item:3107}} , then {{item:3504}} 
Marskmen: {{item:3072}} , then {{item:3031}} , then {{item:3142}} , then {{item:3031}} again

Nerfing Duskblade will, once again, nerf the power of a class's first item spike. What do you expect assassins to build if not Duskblade?
